00:35:12.096 --> 00:35:14.419
mysteriously, assuming it's not murdered.

00:35:15.700 --> 00:35:18.120
But she had two babies and they both died,

00:35:18.120 --> 00:35:21.480
which is obviously a terrible tragedy for
