you're gonna have a term
that's P(innocence).

00:37:01.600 --> 00:37:04.278
That's the prior probability of innocence,

00:37:04.278 --> 00:37:08.615
that's the probability of innocence
before we have any evidence, okay?

00:37:08.615 --> 00:37:13.227
Now there are billions of
mothers in the world, a vast,

00:37:13.227 --> 00:37:17.949
vast majority of them do not
