00:46:15.550 --> 00:46:17.230
And if we knew that thing,

00:46:17.230 --> 00:46:19.990
it may be reasonable to assume
independence conditionally, but

00:46:19.990 --> 00:46:25.570
without that thing, then the earlier
trials give us data that we can use, okay?

00:46:25.570 --> 00:46:26.660
So that's the distinction there.

00:46:26.660 --> 00:46:31.320
All right, last thing is what
